39 (2) Failure to complete and return the card or form shall not diminish any warranty rights
40 or decrease the warranty term.
41 (c) Any warranty of an HVAC system or any component of such system manufactured and
42 issued, sold, or offered for sale by a manufacturer, distributor, or retailer shall not be in any
43 way conditioned upon product registration."
44 SECTION 2.
45 (a) This Act shall become effective on January 1, 2026.
46 (b) This Act shall apply to any warranty of an HVAC system or any component of such
47 system manufactured and issued, sold, or offered for sale by a manufacturer, distributor, or
48 retailer on or after the effective date of this Act and to any modifications or extensions of
49 such warranties issued, sold, or offered for sale on or after such date.
50 SECTION 3.
51 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
